{"tid":2439174,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"iu死左呀!!!!!!南韓演員李知恩驚傳離世家中","createTime":"2021-03-09T05:10:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-09T12:35:01.000Z","uid":173631,"like":1,"dislike":41,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7c5994ac5ddefbe881d627918e3f20cdb2377512","tid":2439174,"uid":173631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T05:10:52.000Z","msg":"南韓演員李知恩驚傳離世家中 享年50歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕南韓女演員李知恩（이지은）今（9日）驚傳離世消息，享年50歲。<br />\n<br />\n首爾中部警察局表示，昨晚（8日）大概8點接獲李知恩的朋友報案，表示聯絡不到對方，警方立刻前往李知恩家中，發現他已經沒有呼吸。李知恩原本和兒子住在一起，但目前兒子正在當兵，李知恩獨自居住。警方表示將驗屍確認死因。<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.hkgolden.media/comment/wz4d5vy5.o2jtdt5ceb2.c5u3051byrb.npw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.hkgolden.media%2Fcomment%2Fwz4d5vy5.o2jtdt5ceb2.c5u3051byrb.npw.jpg&h=c2513b5e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7227524138ebc54b769d5fb77556ed957627ecff","tid":2439174,"uid":143192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T05:12:50.000Z","msg":"50歲"},{"pid":"e264dc1ad82f779131daa7f9db8f5cdb1ec99c43","tid":2439174,"uid":339805,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T05:13:39.000Z","msg":"發布假消息，已經報警<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfb18ba3782675bc11d8037930f852155308ed33","tid":2439174,"uid":199670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T05:14:23.000Z","msg":"iu<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30e164b018cae78cd00ab81f2afb23872bfe32b3","tid":2439174,"uid":366655,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T12:26:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big